# {{lb|en|archaeology|geology|paleontology}} {{initialism of|en|[[year]]s [[before]] [[present]]}}
#* '''2004''' ''Wikipedia article on [[wikipedia:Deluge_(mythology)|Deluge (mythology)]]''
#*: During glacial times, a stretch of level plain joined Australia with New Guinea and enabled humans to walk into Australia. That plain flooded to form the Gulf of Carpentaria, between ''ca'' 12,000 and 10,000 '''ybp'''.
====Usage notes====
A [[year]] [[designation]] [[alternative]] to the [[widely]]-[[used]] but [[Christian]]-[[oriented]] [[designation]]s [[BC]] and [[AD]] and their [[secular]] [[equivalent]]s [[BCE]] and [[CE]]. Used in [[historical]] [[sciences]], especially when the exact number of years is unknown, and where precision and the current year are not significant.
